        "subject": "LU-14006 o2ib: raise bind cap before resolving address",
        "message": "LU-14006 o2ib: raise bind cap before resolving address\n\nIn kiblnd_resolve_addr(), ensure that the current task has\nCAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE before calling rdma_resolve_addr() with a\nprotected source port.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/40127\nLustre-commit: 1e4bd16acfa26a06486ebd3426547502eedefa45\n\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Faaland <faaland1@llnl.gov>\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <jhammond@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0552fdd64648ccb8c74667bd93852697f99f0c33\nReviewed-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
